{
  "name": "cal-merge",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "日曆合併器",
  "category": "H",
  "number": 141,
  "pain_point": "多日曆來源無法統一",
  "commercial": "⚠️",
  "language": "Python",
  "dependencies": [
    "icalendar",
    "caldav",
    "click"
  ],
  "agent_compatible": true,
  "mcp_ready": true,
  "intent_triggers": [
    "我有 Google Calendar 和 Outlook 日曆，想合成一個",
    "多個行事曆來源怎麼統一管理？",
    "幫我把家庭日曆和工作日曆合在一起",
    "不同平台的行事曆要怎麼整合？",
    "想把三個 ics 檔案合成一個完整日曆",
    "跨平台行事曆合併工具",
    "日曆資料分散在不同帳號很麻煩"
  ],
  "examples": [
    {
      "query": "合併 work.ics 和 personal.ics 輸出 merged-calendar.ics",
      "params": {
        "action": "diff",
        "file_a": "work.ics",
        "file_b": "personal.ics",
        "output": "merged-calendar.ics"
      }
    },
    {
      "query": "比對 google.ics 和 outlook.ics 找出衝突的行程",
      "params": {
        "action": "diff",
        "file_a": "google.ics",
        "file_b": "outlook.ics",
        "mode": "conflicts_only"
      }
    },
    {
      "query": "從 CalDAV 伺服器拉取並合併所有日曆",
      "params": {
        "action": "diff",
        "source": "caldav",
        "server_url": "https://caldav.example.com"
      }
    }
  ],
  "params_schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "action": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "file_a": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "file_b": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "mode": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "output": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "server_url": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "source": {
        "type": "string"
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "action"
    ]
  },
  "license": "MIT",
  "status": "available",
  "source": "https://github.com/clibrary-hub/cli-tools/tree/main/manifests/H141-cal-merge"
}